description:
A weak item won from early levels of many labyrinths. Recovers a slight amount of health.
Heals 50 HP.
name: Weak Healing Potion

description:
An intermediate magic item of medium potency, it recovers a decent amount of health while remaing a common find.
Heals 300 HP.

description:
A fairly powerful magic item. It is found in deeper levels of dungeons and recovers a lot of Health.
Heals 1800 HP.
name: Strong Healing Potion

description:
This item offers the mightiest form of physical recovery, found only in very deep labyrinths and very rare. They completely heal any mortal.
Heals 9000 HP.
name: True Healing Potion

description:

Recovers 150 MP.

description:
A fairly powerful magic item. It is found in deeper levels of dungeons and recovers a lot of Mana.
Recovers 750 MP.
name: Strong Mana Potion

description:
This item offers the mightiest form of magical recovery, found only in very deep labyrinths and very rare. They completely fill any mortals' reserve of Mana.
Recovers 2500 MP.
name: True Mana Potion

description: Credits distributed to men that can be given to females when desired. Females can use these credits to lower their tax and/or the price of items. 2 Female Credits equate 1 Gold.

description: A mystical Gear of Magic engulfed in the Mana of Flame. This special Orb is won from the deep depths of the Flame Labyrinth, it's transcendant power is the only known way to truly enhance one's compatibility with Spells of Fire. Consume this item to evolve any of the five Flame Spells to Stage 1 and make them deal more damage!
name: Spell Evolution Orb: Flame -- Stage 1
